@increase_tax
title: Increase tax rate
on-arrival: {! Q.taxes["Q.tax_changed"].rate += 0.1 !}
go-to: change_taxes

[+ name +] – slightly increased.

@decrease_tax
title: Decrease tax rate
on-arrival: {! Q.taxes["Q.tax_changed"].rate -= 0.1 !}
go-to: change_taxes

[+ name +] – slightly decreased.
